        "id": "XbA04hvCiBof"
      },
      "source": [
        "##### **Project Type**    - EDA\n",
        "##### **Contribution**    - Individual\n",
        "##### **Team Member 1 -** Snehal\n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
